own as Fennymere) in Baschurch, Shropshire (derived from Old English <i>fyne</i> ‘mould’ + <i>mere</i> ‘pool, lake’, meaning ‘mouldy lake’). Perhaps also from one or more of the following places in Buckinghamshire: Finemere Wood in Quainton, Fenemore's Farm in Oakley, and Finnamore Farm in Ibstone.","English:"]}]},{"name":"John","type":"FIRST","meanings":["Greek: the Lord gave graciously; whom Jehovah gave; whom Jehovah bestowed."],"variants":[]}],"lifeSummary":"When John Finamore was born about 1350, in Devon, England, United Kingdom, his father, William Finamore, was 25 and his mother, Mrs William Finamore, was 22. He had at least 1 son with Jone Fitz Woulfe."},"et":{"Abt 1350–":"umbes 1350–Surnud","1350–Male":"1350–Surnud","1354–Female":"1354–Surnud","1376–Male":"1376–Surnud","1327–Male":"1327–Surnud","1330–Female":"1330–Surnud","1327":"1327","Abt 1350":"umbes 1350","1376":"1376","1354":"1354","1330":"1330","1350":"1350","Fenne,Devon,Eng":"Devon, Inglismaa, United Kingdom","Fenne, Devon, England":"Devon, Inglismaa, United Kingdom"},"fi":{"Abt 1350–":"noin 1350–Kuollut","1350–Male":"1350–Kuollut","1354–Female":"1354–Kuollut","1376–Male":"1376–Kuollut","1327–Male":"1327–Kuollut","1330–Female":"1330–Kuollut","1327":"1327","Abt 1350":"noin 1350","1376":"1376","1354":"1354","1330":"1330","1350":"1350","Fenne,Devon,Eng":"Devon, Englanti, Yhdistynyt kuningaskunta","Fenne, Devon, England":"Devon, Englanti, Yhdistynyt kuningaskunta"},"fr":{"Abt 1350–":"environ 1350–Décédé","1350–Male":"1350–Décédé","1354–Female":"1354–Décédée","1376–Male":"1376–Décédé","1327–Male":"1327–Décédé","1330–Female":"1330–Décédée","1327":"1327","Abt 1350":"environ 1350","1376":"1376","1354":"1354","1330":"1330","1350":"1350","Fenne,Devon,Eng":"Devon, Angleterre, Royaume-Uni","Fenne, Devon, England":"Devon, Angleterre, Royaume-Uni","lifeSummary":"Lorsque John Finamore est né environ 1350, à Devon, Angleterre, Royaume-Uni, son père, William Finamore, avait 25 ans et sa mère, Mrs William Finamore, a